{"tid":423283,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Clone完Windows去SSD, 為什麼仍然幫我用HD開機？救教","createTime":"2017-10-03T18:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T13:02:06.000Z","uid":126323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"aba11ca9461bd66ef10c0f6587d9d8ec24f54627","tid":423283,"uid":126323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T18:38:20.000Z","msg":"我的Notebook拆了光碟盤裝了SSD<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/04/023608_cfc1fd8a6bd4c5848dbb87d8dec94695.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F04%2F023608_cfc1fd8a6bd4c5848dbb87d8dec94695.jpg&h=2779e836&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而且已經Clone了去SSD那裡<br />\nBoot Sequence 也調了用SSD開機<br />\n就係唔知點解佢仍然用HD開機<br />\n有冇人知道點解決？<br />\n救指教一下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4154b367d6653c4b5c4a1380442566e2dd2e26e6","tid":423283,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T18:45:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我的Notebook拆了光碟盤裝了SSD<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/04/023608_cfc1fd8a6bd4c5848dbb87d8dec94695.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F04%2F023608_cfc1fd8a6bd4c5848dbb87d8dec94695.jpg&h=2779e836&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而且已經Clone了去SSD那裡<br />\nBoot Sequence 也調了用SSD開機<br />\n就係唔知點解佢仍然用HD開機<br />\n有冇人知道點解決？<br />\n救指教一下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDisconnect hard drive first to try<br />\nMaybe the clone fails or the boot record not cloned properly"},{"pid":"be4323004782c69eef6881c3d3ee458f5643bacd","tid":423283,"uid":126323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T19:21:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我的Notebook拆了光碟盤裝了SSD<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/04/023608_cfc1fd8a6bd4c5848dbb87d8dec94695.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F04%2F023608_cfc1fd8a6bd4c5848dbb87d8dec94695.jpg&h=2779e836&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而且已經Clone了去SSD那裡<br />\nBoot Sequence 也調了用SSD開機<br />\n就係唔知點解佢仍然用HD開機<br />\n有冇人知道點解決？<br />\n救指教一下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDisconnect hard drive first to try<br />\nMaybe the clone fails or the boot record not cloned properly</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/04/031955_9e2db62846ee60e11be618a9f9567690.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F04%2F031955_9e2db62846ee60e11be618a9f9567690.jpg&h=f29397ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我見佢依然係C Drive果到有個Windows Logo<br />\nE Drive係SSD (已經Clone左C Drive落黎)"},{"pid":"4e430e850b5ba079b1e60d2d842c261e2ecbf579","tid":423283,"uid":13645,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T19:23:07.000Z","msg":"bios 都唔識用就咪撚學人diy 啦屌"},{"pid":"aec9602deb8e842459f144910e7f33e67e248e9d","tid":423283,"uid":43842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T19:27:59.000Z","msg":"個boot partition依然係HDD<br />\nClone果陣無搬埋過去SSD<br />\n抄哂重要野之後重裝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de977b8ab2d11780dbc789545d7df81e14b41a07","tid":423283,"uid":1696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T19:36:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我的Notebook拆了光碟盤裝了SSD<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/04/023608_cfc1fd8a6bd4c5848dbb87d8dec94695.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F04%2F023608_cfc1fd8a6bd4c5848dbb87d8dec94695.jpg&h=2779e836&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而且已經Clone了去SSD那裡<br />\nBoot Sequence 也調了用SSD開機<br />\n就係唔知點解佢仍然用HD開機<br />\n有冇人知道點解決？<br />\n救指教一下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDisconnect hard drive first to try<br />\nMaybe the clone fails or the boot record not cloned properly</blockquote><br />\n應該唔係呢個問題<br />\n你睇下佢bios 做緊d咩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d2cf75a733382ff008aefea20d2438542e382a7","tid":423283,"uid":126323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T22:19:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>bios 都唔識用就咪撚學人diy 啦屌</blockquote><br />\n就係想有人指教一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b59d0ea2d94fe81326b702820dd79c3a8cbe90","tid":423283,"uid":126323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T22:21:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我的Notebook拆了光碟盤裝了SSD<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/04/023608_cfc1fd8a6bd4c5848dbb87d8dec94695.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F04%2F023608_cfc1fd8a6bd4c5848dbb87d8dec94695.jpg&h=2779e836&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而且已經Clone了去SSD那裡<br />\nBoot Sequence 也調了用SSD開機<br />\n就係唔知點解佢仍然用HD開機<br />\n有冇人知道點解決？<br />\n救指教一下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDisconnect hard drive first to try<br />\nMaybe the clone fails or the boot record not cloned properly</blockquote><br />\n應該唔係呢個問題<br />\n你睇下佢bios 做緊d咩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以講下邊到出錯嗎？"},{"pid":"f4a332245d135ffb9c8ad0336c67669439d38db5","tid":423283,"uid":1696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T23:53:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我的Notebook拆了光碟盤裝了SSD<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/04/023608_cfc1fd8a6bd4c5848dbb87d8dec94695.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F04%2F023608_cfc1fd8a6bd4c5848dbb87d8dec94695.jpg&h=2779e836&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而且已經Clone了去SSD那裡<br />\nBoot Sequence 也調了用SSD開機<br />\n就係唔知點解佢仍然用HD開機<br />\n有冇人知道點解決？<br />\n救指教一下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDisconnect hard drive first to try<br />\nMaybe the clone fails or the boot record not cloned properly</blockquote><br />\n應該唔係呢個問題<br />\n你睇下佢bios 做緊d咩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以講下邊到出錯嗎？</blockquote><br />\n你仲set緊用hdd開機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHGST 轉返ssd先<br />\n如果都係唔得先用上面個方法"},{"pid":"18a4788a1264c83ec3797eee2d63264c7dc537cc","tid":423283,"uid":126323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T03:37:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我的Notebook拆了光碟盤裝了SSD<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/04/023608_cfc1fd8a6bd4c5848dbb87d8dec94695.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F04%2F023608_cfc1fd8a6bd4c5848dbb87d8dec94695.jpg&h=2779e836&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而且已經Clone了去SSD那裡<br />\nBoot Sequence 也調了用SSD開機<br />\n就係唔知點解佢仍然用HD開機<br />\n有冇人知道點解決？<br />\n救指教一下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDisconnect hard drive first to try<br />\nMaybe the clone fails or the boot record not cloned properly</blockquote><br />\n應該唔係呢個問題<br />\n你睇下佢bios 做緊d咩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以講下邊到出錯嗎？</blockquote><br />\n你仲set緊用hdd開機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHGST 轉返ssd先<br />\n如果都係唔得先用上面個方法</blockquote><br />\n佢係<br />\nODD連住SSD<br />\nHDD/SSD連住HDD<br />\n成行成行咁上落<br />\n冇得將HDD/SSD改做SSD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fccde7acc0badce68ada01f5eaa2dfddbfe781b6","tid":423283,"uid":148531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T06:21:06.000Z","msg":"因為你ssd無bootloader<br />\n<br />\n齋clone無用 因為佢無clone開啟程式"},{"pid":"bd15949136a6919bf3321410f3f3eb9ec0f6ee12","tid":423283,"uid":111320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T06:26:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為你ssd無bootloader<br />\n<br />\n齋clone無用 因為佢無clone開啟程式</blockquote><br />\n唔係用clone zilla 成隻clone 就OK?<br />\n我以前hdd 換ssd 好似都係咁做"},{"pid":"ca50ec3b3a75b2cc6f826b62ce11f40203d34632","tid":423283,"uid":126323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T09:29:46.000Z","msg":"我試過拆左個HDD落黎<br />\n只係Boot SSD開唔到<br />\n可能真係Clone少左野<br />\n依家用緊另一個Clone Software試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca70ae730e18ca2aed913d3b036e3a4d6e5b9133","tid":423283,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T09:37:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">我的Notebook拆了光碟盤裝了SSD</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/04/023608_cfc1fd8a6bd4c5848dbb87d8dec94695.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F04%2F023608_cfc1fd8a6bd4c5848dbb87d8dec94695.jpg&h=2779e836&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而且已經Clone了去SSD那裡<br />\nBoot Sequence 也調了用SSD開機<br />\n就係唔知點解佢仍然用HD開機<br />\n有冇人知道點解決？<br />\n救指教一下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n插odd位未必可以用黎當boot drive(應該話多數唔得)"},{"pid":"4867e4619eb3817539cf48fcd6c1f0294af6c4c5","tid":423283,"uid":19165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T12:48:00.000Z","msg":"我試過同你有同一個問題, 後尾google過發現有D notebook可能係鎖死左隻HDD做primary boot up, 連係BIOS改都無用, 所以最後都係先係部desktop PC confirm左隻SSD係well clone, 換隻HDD去desktop PC度format, 搞掂後再放返入去notebook"},{"pid":"5afee813bf6d25667da70f7face1daf9c4b0a058","tid":423283,"uid":2474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:02:06.000Z","msg":"砍掉重裝啦"}]}